                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-47-defend469 t18150405-47-punish260"></join>
               Confined two years in Newgate
            </rs>, and at the expiration of that time, to <rs id="t18150405-47-punish261" type="punishmentDescription">
