                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150405-47-defend469 t18150405-47-punish261"></join>
               find sureties for two years good behaviour
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
